  "lyrics": [
    {
      "t": 32740,
      "text": "Her parents said, \"Girl, don't leave home\"",
      "end": 36600
    },
    {
      "t": 36600,
      "text": "But her heart kept cheering her on",
      "end": 40600
    },
    {
      "t": 40600,
      "text": "She had a real good man, a steady job",
      "end": 44810
    },
    {
      "t": 44810,
      "text": "But the two of them just weren't in her heart",
      "end": 48720
    },
    {
      "t": 48720,
      "text": "She only wanted to be close to me",
      "end": 52330
    },
    {
      "t": 52330,
      "text": "To give me the love she knew someday I'd need",
      "end": 56290
    },
    {
      "t": 56290,
      "text": "But I kept saying, \"Girl, you're wrong, go home\"",
      "end": 68890
    },
    {
      "t": 68890,
      "text": "Long days, short nights when you're on the road",
      "end": 73070
    },
    {
      "t": 73070,
      "text": "For a pretty girl, it's a heavy load",
      "end": 77150
    },
    {
      "t": 77150,
      "text": "And even so, who'll pay your fare?",
      "end": 80900
    },
    {
      "t": 80900,
      "text": "She said, \"I'll make it on a wing and a prayer\"",
      "end": 85030
    },
    {
      "t": 85030,
      "text": "She only wanted to be close to me",
      "end": 88540
    },
    {
      "t": 88540,
      "text": "To give me the love she knew someday I'd need",
      "end": 92660
    },
    {
      "t": 92660,
      "text": "But I kept saying, \"Girl, you're wrong, go home\"",
      "end": 105190
    },
    {
      "t": 105190,
      "text": "She said I had no right to tell her how life should be",
      "end": 113280
    },
    {
      "t": 113280,
      "text": "Especially when the only one she ever cared about in life was me",
      "end": 118800
    },
    {
      "t": 118800,
      "text": "But she agreed to go along with my final word",
      "end": 133500
    },
    {
      "t": 133500,
      "text": "As fate would have life come around",
      "end": 137360
    },
    {
